<h3>Online registrations are now closed. If you still need to register for classes (or pay for classes already entered), please go to the Village Hall on Thursday 12th August between 17:00 and 19:30, or Friday 13th between 16:00 and 19:00, where you will also be able to collect your exhibitor cards.
